DE_Cemetery by Kev_Boy
kevindesmet@yahoo.com

Background: A month after 6-6-06, the 19th angel guarding hell fell, and the dead walked the earth... on zombie servers.

Terrorists: We must bomb the holiest places on this British country-side cemetery. For here lurks great evil and if we do not destroy it, its overwhelming aura will soon cause the dead to walk the earth, for hell is full!

Counter-Terrorists: When killing a dozen hostages in another screw-up... we decided to stop by for a quick prayer, while we got reports of superstitious terrorists wanting to bomb this place!

In the laughable event the dead would walk the earth like they proclaim, longing to 'swallow our souls'... Come Get Some!

This is a little fun map with - more or less^^ - fun elements. It has three floors - one on open air, two inside and one of them with water. It also has a lot of pillars and pillarlike elements. Have fun with them.

The NAV file is created when you start a server with bots on this map.

This map is based in a large prison. One bomb site is in the laundry room and the other is in the cafeteria. There are many different routes around the map. I created custom decals to mark the way to the bomb sites. The map is best when players work together to defend or assault the bomb sites. More screen shots are avalible at my web site. -www.rickets007.com- de_cellblock_f

"Brought to you by novalin, maker or de_residentevil.
novalin has been working on this original map for months (it actually started as a Hostage rescue map). It has been thoroughly play tested through 9 beta versions and is a favorite on our server. This map is best suited for 16-20 players. Game play is excellent. We have found this to be one of the most even maps available. It usually starts with either side winning 4-5 straight rounds, and then the other team makes a comeback. Tonight I added up the stats on our server and 720 rounds were played, and 360 were won by the T’s and 360 were won by CT’s. Please give it a try, you won’t be sorry." [Kas]

Created by dF|novalin / Brian Riggsbee

Email: novalin@gmail.com

Web: www.dangerforce.com

Highly modified version of a golden eye cave map.. I converted the middle of the foundation from GE to a source map and built around it creating a balanced playable bomb map. I took my time and tried to be creative with the lighting and placement of the models.. At the same time having the clash points some what work out between the teams... Also kept optimization in mind for good frame rates... Inspired by de_volare and de_laguna.

- Headshot-only everywhere, except at spawnpoints, so don´t camp too much ;)
- 2 Bombplaces
- MANY places to die ;)
- hf & gl !

Smaller version of de_cathedrill_pro. Exactly this is original map with shorter nave (longer main hall) and shorter transept (both halls crossing longer main hall). I made this next version of map by request of FPSbanana member, who complained about size of map and low framerate. Gameplay is faster now and framerate was increased of a bit. I also removed horses in halls crossing, they didn't fit to theme of map, like someone complained with pro version. Enjoy my map
